We have the following property :
#proposition[
  If (q,a) is the question-answer pair of a winning stategy for the game $C_5$, this is equivalent to the existence of a solution of $Π$ under question $q$ and such that $forall v,space "let" {e_i}_i = N(v), space out_v (sol(v, e_1),dots,sol(v, e_Δ)) = a_v$, i.e. the output of $Π$ for each node is the answer of the corresponding player.
