This proposition is not very interesting, it just says that the game is encode in the black-white formalism. But now we can use the tools of the black-white formalism to analyze the game.

What means that $Π$ is 0 round solvable ? this means that each node need to set a label on its incident edges without knowing every thing else, without knowing the label or either the name of the other node incident to him. This create a kind of language that will be $[01]^5$, the language of all the possible 0,1 label of the 5 nodes. So the chance that the node create an output that is a solution of $Π$ is very low.

And what means that $Π$ is 1 round solvable ? If the question is for exemple $q = (1,0,0,1,0)$, each node with question $1$ will send during the communication step an order to the node next to him, and because the question is such that the node next to him have question $0$ and don't send order, there are no contradiction order ! Then in 1 round communication we can wins this game with probability 1. Know we are intersest in the case the question is $q = (1,1,1,1,1)$. We can do the following stategy : if my question is $1$ and the question of my neighbor is $1 1$, this means that i am in the case where $q = (1,1,1,1,1)$, so i can simply output $1$ and win because everyone do the same, if my neighbor is $0 0$ i output $0$ and if my question is $0$ and output $0$. This strategy win the game in 1 round of communication !

So this conclude that this notion of communication is too powerful, it express nothing !

